pageContext.claim: “One of the reasons we need Great Border Security is that Mexico’s murder rate in 2017 increased by 27% to 31,174 people killed, a record! The Democrats want Open Borders. I want Maximum Border Security and respect for ICE and our great Law Enforcement Professionals!”
pageContext.analysis: Undocumented migration from Mexico has been negative for 10 years. More people are going back to Mexico than are entering the United States.
